These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, time-travel, superhero, adventure
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bus, ship, scooter
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
2. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
3. the person driving the bus is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
5. the person driving the scooter is between the person driving the bus and the person driving the ship##2
6. the person watching adventure movies is the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | horror     | superhero | time-travel |
| Transport     | airplane     | ship | scooter  | bus      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, folk, blues, trance
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, taxi, bike, van
1. the fan of folk is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
2. the person driving the van is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of trance is on the left of the person driving the van##1
4. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
5. the fan of blues is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | disco | folk    | trance     | blues  |
| Transport     | motorbike    | bike | taxi | van |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, gospel, metal, indie
4 different pets are kept: turtle, dog, guinea-pig, pony
1. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3
2. the fan of gospel is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the fan of indie##1
4. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel   | metal   | disco  | indie |
| Pet           | dog | pony | guinea-pig | turtle  |

