.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, drawing, video-games, filmmaking
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, polish, spanish, japanese
1. the japanese is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the spanish##2
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
4. the spanish is on the left or right of the japanese##3
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
6. the australian is on the right of the polish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | drawing | sudoku | filmmaking | video-games  |
| Nationality   | polish  | australian   | japanese  | spanish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, lemonade, juice, mirinda
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, chess, writing, card-games
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
5. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | sprite    | lemonade   | juice | mirinda    |
| Hobby      | chess | photography | writing       | card-games |

