.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, cola, sprite, milk
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, scooter, skateboard, ship
1. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is between the person driving the ship and the person drinking sprite##2
3. the person driving the taxi is between the person driving the skateboard and the person drinking lemonade##2
4. the person driving the ship is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | lemonade | sprite | milk | cola |
| Transport   | scooter | taxi  | skateboard    | ship  |

