2. the pakistani is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the car##1
4. the japanese is between the american and the russian##2
5. the person driving the subway is the person driving the subway##1
6. the person driving the subway is between the person driving the car and the russian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Nationality   | pakistani | russian | japanese | american     |
| Transport     | scooter | bus  | subway   | car |

