.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, photography, hiking, card-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, documentary, martial-arts, sports
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person watching documentary movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
5. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
6. the person watching documentary movies is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Hobby         | card-games | hiking | chess | photography   |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | martial-arts | time-travel      | sports |

