2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is baseball is the owner of the frog##1
4. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left or far right##3
6. the owner of the dog is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who's sport is golf##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Pet     | rabbit | dog   | pony      | frog      |
| Sport   | ice-hockey     | weightlifting | golf | baseball |

