.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, woodworking, photography, board-games
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, bus, train, subway
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
3. the person driving the subway is the person who's hobby is photography##1
4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
5. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
6. the person driving the train is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby       | rock-climbing | photography | board-games    | woodworking      |
| Transport   | train       | subway       | bus | motorbike |

