.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, coffee, sprite, lemonade
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, basketball, cricket, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
6. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
7. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | coffee     | iced-tea     | sprite          | lemonade |
| Sport      | volleyball | basketball | lacrosse | cricket  |

 